      <title>澳大利亚监管机构将加大力度保护消费者储蓄</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-regulator-ramp-up-focus-protecting-consumer-savings-2024-11-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚企业监管机构周四表示，明年其工作重点将是严厉打击金融领域的不法行为，保护首当其冲受到生活成本上涨压力的消费者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/australia-regulator-ramp-up-focus-protecting-consumer-savings-2024-11-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 05:03:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
